snippet.title: Best VGM 1144 - Rayman - Pink Plant Woods Area 2
snippet.description:
See also:
Best VGM 1538 - https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=o0t8vHJtaKk

A collection of my favorite videogame music. Note that most of them are from games I played so I might miss some great ones from games I never played.

Playstation / PC / Jaguar / Saturn
Rayman (1995)
Pink Plant Woods Area 2
Stéphane Bellanger & Pete Anthony
